        "evidence": "<p>Addition of selected points.</p>",
        "facts": "<p><strong>Score interpretation</strong></p>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n<table class=\"table table-bordered table-hover\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Risk Group</th>\n<th>Score</th>\n<th>2.5-month rate of VTE</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Low</td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>0.3-0.8%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Intermediate</td>\n<td>1 - 2</td>\n<td>1.8-2.0%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>High</td>\n<td>&ge;3</td>\n<td>6.7-7.1%</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>",
